{"title":"公社儿歌","authors":["金近"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":12,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社儿歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上的自来水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上接下毛竹来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出清清的自来水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通到食堂里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧茶煮饭又洗菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通到澡堂里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清水日夜流得快。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这水要比城里好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水哪有这样美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝衣组"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈工钱刚领到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买布给我做棉袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到缝衣组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器突突跳，两个钟头就做好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一点费用也不要。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将来穿衣不要钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个办法更加好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理发馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社办个理发馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家理发不要钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月理两次，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干净又好看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的头发剪得短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样子看看更勇敢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上发出一阵香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝴蝶蜜蜂跟我转。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}